      "writtenOn": "2020-02-06T21:01:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "testApp is internal. No other package (and no other test binary) will attempt to start servers on the same ports, so it does not present a problem now. Also notice how this package is called: \"integrationtests\", i.e. we don\u0027t expect integration tests in other packages.\n\nI\u0027ve added a TODO to address this when server.Server exposes the ports",
